node.text:
Waddap! It’s Talking Thursday! Woohoo! I know what day it is! 🤣

So today, let’s talk about light. I find it very interesting how these 3 pictures are taken at the same location but with just a change of angles and how you move the camera, you can play with natural light to give you different vibes in each photo!
.
Kinda cool huh? Which one do you prefer out of the 3?
.
Besides playing around with light, we also ate a cute Totoro cream puff! I was lucky that my airbnb was a nice walk away from this cafe & the cream puffs are not only cute, they taste good too. 🤤 Ah... I sure miss travelling. 🥺
.
#throwbackJapan2019 #stayhomesg #leicaCL #zeiss50mmf15zm #stayhomeforsg #circuitbreakersg
@zanthrea Saaammmeee. It shone down so prettily.
Beautiful my friend 🌷😍💫 and clearly 1 because of your beautiful smile 😊
@lastminuteitinerary 🤣🤣 The first picture’s my personal favourite too!
I love all 3 of them but I think the first picture has to be my favourite 😍

@mahmoudzaki1997 🤣🤣🤣 I love your creative response! 💕 🤣🤣 I wish I could reach into the fourth photo & take the cream puff out of it. Thanks for always being so kind! Many well wishes to you & your family as well! 😁
1+2+3=SUPEEEEEEERB BEAUTY, This is the answer equation!!! Can I take the fourth photo and run away? Hahahaaaa! Love this share, hope you a lovely time and wishing you and your family are veeery well!
@so.gelly Japan is my favorite holiday destination. Tokyo is my most favorite Asian city in the world, but I also like Hakodate too.
@lagoon Haha yup! Has a soft vibe! I want a totoro cream puff anytime but they are pretty expensive. 🤣
All very nice but 2 is softer all round. And I want a totoro cream puff now❕
Dé Cartagena Valparaíso Chile te amo bb cuidate mucho😍😍
